ВұCORE-THESIS
LLM-contextвҶ’linear-cost($3-15/M-tokens)+quadratic-attention
Domain-knowledge(YAML,MD,rules,entities)вҶ’high-structural-redundancy
вҳ…INSIGHT:gap-between(human-written-density,transformer-consumed-density)вҶ’exploitable
ANALOGY:MP3вҶ’psychoacoustic-model|CtxPackвҶ’transformer-perceptual-model
CODEC-TYPE:deterministic,open-source,text-based,inspectable,versionable

ВұCTX-FORMAT вҳ…FORMAL-SPEC:PEG-grammar(105-rules)
PRINCIPLES:[plain-text(UTF-8,diffable,git-friendly),multi-resolution,deterministic,format-aware(not-model-specific)]
CONFORMANCE-LEVELS:L1(compressed-prose)вҶ’L2(semantic-graph)вҶ’L3(abstract-gist)
OPERATORS:[В§(header),Вұ(section),вҶ’(flow/transition),|(alternative),+(conjunction),вҳ…(high-salience),вҡ (warning),@(cross-ref),В¬(negation)]
OPERATOR-DESIGN:Unicode-operatorsвҶ’single/two-token-unitsвҶ’high-info-density-per-token
PARSER:recursive-descent,pure-Python(410-lines),zero-depsвҶ’frozen-dataclass-AST
AST-NODES:[CTXDocument,Header,Section,KeyValue,InlineList,PlainLine,QuotedBlock]
вҡ TOKENIZER-NOTE:token-counts-use-whitespace-split-approximation|cross-tokenizer-variance-expected(<10%)

ВұPACKER PIPELINE:DiscoverвҶ’ParseвҶ’EntityResolveвҶ’ConflictDetectвҶ’ScoreвҶ’Compress
STAGE-1-DISCOVER:walk-corpus,classify(.yaml/.yml,.md),load-ctxpack.yaml-config
STAGE-2-PARSE:YAML-subset-parser(722-lines,stdlib-only,В¬anchors,В¬tags)|MD-heading/list-extractorвҶ’IR(entities,fields,warnings)
STAGE-3-RESOLVE:exact-matchвҶ’case-insensitiveвҶ’aliasвҶ’singular/plural|field-dedup-by(key+value)|provenance-tracked
STAGE-4-CONFLICT:retention-policy|null-policy|type-mismatch|PII-classificationвҶ’вҡ warnings
STAGE-5-SALIENCE:entity_score=(source_countГ—1.0+cross_refsГ—2.0+warningsГ—1.5)Г—golden_boost(1.5)|field-boost:[вҳ…:2.0x,вҡ :1.5x,IDENTIFIER/PII/MATCH-RULES:1.3x]|sort-descendingвҶ’exploit-attention(primacy+recency)
STAGE-6-COMPRESS:IRвҶ’CTXDocument-AST(bottom-up)|type-specific-rulesвҶ’operator-notation
вҳ…SCOPE-INFERENCE:entity-description-pattern-matchвҶ’enrich-identifiers(e.g.unique:true+desc:"one-per-merchant"вҶ’unique-per-merchant)|disable-via(--strict)
IMPL:pure-Python,zero-deps,2407-lines,10-modules|CLI:ctxpack-pack|API:from-ctxpack.core.packer-import-pack

ВұEVAL-METHODOLOGY
AXES:[compression-efficiency(source/compressed-ratio),information-fidelity(Q&A-correctness)]
вҳ…GOLDEN-SET:10-source-files(4-entity-YAML,2-rule-YAML,3-MD,1-config)|4-entities(CUSTOMER,ORDER,PAYMENT,PRODUCT)|690-source-tokens|2-planted-conflicts
QUESTIONS:25-total[Easy:7(direct-lookup),Medium:11(multi-field-inference),Hard:7(cross-doc,adversarial)]|5-adversarial(2-hallucination-traps,2-low-salience,1-cross-entity-negation)
BASELINES:[raw-stuffing(1x,upper-bound),ctxpack-L2(ours),llm-summary(same-token-budget),naive-truncation(first-N-words,floor)]
GRADING-DUAL:[rule-based(keyword-match,60%-threshold),llm-as-judge(CORRECT/INCORRECT)]|primary-metric:llm-judge(cross-model)
вҳ…PROMPT-EQUALIZATION(v0.2.1):identical-system+user-msgs-both-providers|QA-sys:"precise-Q&A-assistant"|judge-sys:"expert-grader"|temperature:0
SELF-JUDGING:each-model-judges-own-answers|cross-model-agreement:92%(23/25)
JUDGE-VARIANCE:Вұ4-12pp-between-independent-runs
MODELS:[Claude-Sonnet-4.6(Anthropic),GPT-4o(OpenAI)]|same-.ctx-files,same-questions,same-scales
SCALING-CORPORA:synthetic-multi-domain(retail,logistics,healthcare,fintech,HR,marketing)|scales:[690,1202,4098,15244,37411]-tokens
TOTAL-COST:~$30(~2500-API-calls,~8M-input-tokens)|60%-attributable-to-raw-37K

